      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "场设灵堂。〖牌子〗。门子上，打扫灵堂。罗春上，罗妻抱罗通上。",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
